{"tid":1435972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（獨媒特約報導）傳黑社會周日北角斬人 民陣報案促警部署","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:58:30.000Z","uid":285899,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9de53f663937a0aa1013cfaacbc27f1552789536","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066360?fbclid=IwAR2StR0sdA64mRPtly429NNK_Yi7w6ZxT4UXeiCrC0pfX909FFapVFwdz0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066360%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2StR0sdA64mRPtly429NNK_Yi7w6ZxT4UXeiCrC0pfX909FFapVFwdz0Q&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=f58aa8c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066360%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2StR0sdA64mRPtly429NNK_Yi7w6ZxT4UXeiCrC0pfX909FFapVFwdz0Q&h=30faef1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066360?fbclid=IwAR2StR0sdA64mRPtly429NNK_Yi7w6ZxT4UXeiCrC0pfX909FFapVFwdz0Q</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）有市民於星期日發起東區遊行，原擬由維園遊行至北角，並於終點渣華道遊樂場集會，但遭警方反對，只准於維園舉行集會。近日傳出消息，指有黑社會人士計劃周日於北角襲擊身穿黑衣的示威者。民陣副召集人陳皓桓及何啟明今日（8月9日）到北角警署報案，呼籲警方盡快部署。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓稱，透過社交媒體得知，約千名疑似社團人士將於遊行期間襲擊身穿黑衣的示威者。陳指報案時，警員主動詢問事件始末，可見警方早已得悉事件。他呼籲警方盡快部署，以保障市民的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n陳續稱，過往多次大型示威活動，包括7月21日在元朗、8月5日在北角及荃灣，均有疑似有背景人士，手持刀、棍等武器追打市民，導致人心惶惶。8月5日陳在荃灣眾安街用餐時，亦親眼目擊白衣刀手襲擊兩名市民，斬斷其手筋及腳筋，傷者大量流血，需要送院搶救。他批評警方執法不力，至今只就7.21元朗恐襲拘捕了20人，難以令市民信服。他指，作為一名普通市民，報警是唯一能做的事，希望警方負起執法責任，盡快將兇徒繩之於法。"},{"pid":"99cd22b21699e4db91d6e39021d189cfd8661d18","tid":1435972,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"真正和理非用處 , 警就報左 , 你一唔做野就唔好怪市民同外國反你"},{"pid":"049dd4c4b065a3c13b20a1119d7f44ac1c91c4c4","tid":1435972,"uid":136958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"民陣同泛民最應該和理非能力極大化 你唔迫 對家唔撚驚 你迫 就好大迴響反應 你要知道和理非係好疊馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11e4f14dfb0d1ebd64fee54a6d6ba181a6999ae","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"推到記者問"},{"pid":"29d4a62384f3a02891285f406796fa48d1262a32","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"推到記者問"},{"pid":"19ec7ab554f8fd3bc1bb12aaff7ce9a2fbaa098e","tid":1435972,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"荃灣都好似喺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba885ea6bd8b9f19a25b7a8fda48f899898207b4","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"推到記者問"},{"pid":"4eda6d85097b6baa633e38e4554861c38c32f1e3","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"推到記者問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09361b76a4cff80529211698f50eb3a2486ea6ae","tid":1435972,"uid":119283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"推到D警察當住全香港人清晰有件咁嘅傳聞。一定要一定要。"},{"pid":"7addd4d264db1bb46cc59979187f065b592746eb","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"推到記者問"},{"pid":"f752144f6bb4ea00c8080f14f51a4e5b2698c1ac","tid":1435972,"uid":263094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"如何佢地唔處理<br />\n<br />\n如果話網上傳唔可以做證據的話<br />\n上次佢試laser pointer時都係搵連登post做證據<br />\n<br />\n甘佢就自打嘴巴，要承受選擇性執法，違反警例，防礙司法公正"},{"pid":"aca367211daae608a112100ceba4247e1a16efe7","tid":1435972,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd746c6781eb0d08cd58217f5fca0b69e3e2c8c1","tid":1435